Class Selectable

java.lang.Object
  mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.Selectable
Direct Known Subclasses:
NonBlockingObjectChannel, SelectableFutureResult, SelectableNormSession
public abstract class Selectable
extends Object

An object that can originate signals to one or more SelectableSets to which they belong.
